	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你问我在干什么？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在做
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />做这个讲究一鼓作气！<delay frames="40" />
当你决定要做的时候，<delay8 />
就要一下子全搞定！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />专心致志做DIY的时候，<delay20 />
这种感觉就像是<delay8 />
骑着摩托车飞驰一样。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了！<delay20 />你要不要也试着做做看？<delay frames="40" />
