	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然这么说，<delay20 />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你现在<delay8 />已经拿不下东西了呀。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还是之后<delay8 />再来找我吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿嘿，<delay20 />我就猜到会有这种情况发生，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />已经事先准备好手册了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来，<delay8 />别客气，拿着吧！</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尝试自己制作还挺有趣的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="1" />你看起来就心灵手巧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定可以比我做得更好！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay20 />记着<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
制作方法的手册，我就交给你啦！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果可以，<delay8 />希望你能把它也传给你的朋友。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经<delay8 />记住了这个做法，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />如果有人想学的话，<delay20 />
我也愿意教给别人。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家都来<delay20 />DIY制作<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定就会成为一种潮流呢！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />写有<delay20 /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
做法的手册，我已经提前准备好了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在交给你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要想制作它的话，<delay20 />
首先要拥有南瓜～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如趁此机会，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也试试种植南瓜吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">如果想要<delay8 />对它进行改造的话，<delay8 />
就需要相应颜色的
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要种植足够多的南瓜，
慢慢就会有不同颜色的南瓜长出来，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就当作打理家庭菜园，好好加油吧。</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />你过来拿<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚才没能给你的东西了啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那你现在快收好吧！</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />你已经知道<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这份手册了啊。</message>
	<message label="034" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样也好。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我手上<delay20 />正好有多余的<colour id="1" />南瓜<colour id="65535" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就<delay8 />拿着吧！</message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望这<colour id="1" />南瓜<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />可以让你
